        "id": "a05dd4de.c6c918",
        "type": "subflow",
        "name": "Dataverse token (client credentials)",
        "info": "Gets an access token for Microsoft Dataverse using the Microsoft identity platform v2.0 client-credentials flow and caches it.\nEnv vars required (set on the subflow *instance*):\n- TENANT_ID: your Entra tenant GUID\n- D365_ORG_URL: e.g., https://contoso.crm4.dynamics.com\n- CLIENT_ID (cred)\n- CLIENT_SECRET (cred)\n\nStores in flow context:\n- dv_at  : access token string\n- dv_exp : expiry (epoch ms)\n- dv_org : org base URL\n\nOutput: passes msg through after ensuring a valid token is cached.",
